name: Spiritum Portals - Aphgan
description: The White Sands Spiritum color schemas were harnessed from photographs taken at White Sands National Monument. A mystical beach, the remnants of an ancient sea, in between two mountains, used as a nuclear missile test range -- the stories they tell us are too odd to be true, and surely the lore of White Sands is a portal into the history they would have us believe. Let the crystally whites, the lone cactus, and the sweeping blue sky of White Sands be a portal into the your own reality.
